HEADWORD: Angleworm
<hw>An"gle*worm`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A earthworm of the genus <gen>Lumbricus</gen>, frequently used by
anglers for bait. See <er>Earthworm</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Anglian</ent>⟦br⟧
